cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "CCA-Audit"
abstract: >-
  A multi-agent code audit and fix pipeline for Claude Code that verifies every finding against
  the real code before acting on it, backed by cca_checks — a deterministic verification layer
  (pyright, pytest, semgrep, and Hypothesis-driven metamorphic and substrate-differential
  properties) that settles claims with reproducible evidence instead of a second LLM opinion.
authors:
  - alias: "GiulioDER"
